  schema:name "Rosaceae" ;
  schema:description "Rose family — ~90 genera, ~2,500 species. Diagnostic 5 petals, numerous stamens, hypanthium (floral cup). Extraordinary fruit diversity — drupe (cherry, peach), pome (apple, pear), aggregate (raspberry, blackberry), achene (strawberry). Major temperate fruit family economically and ornamentally." ;
